body.name: Cozy Castle Kitchen Buffet Cabinet, Kitchen Storage Cabinet with 3 Doors and 3 Drawers, Accent Buffet Sideboard for Kitchen and Living Room, Black
features: 【Elegent Modern Design】This Buffet Cabinet combination of warm oak wood grain tones and pure white is ideal for creating your own cozy nest. This kitchen buffet cabinet can meet both aesthetic and functional needs. It can be placed not only in the entryway, but also in the kitchen, bedroom, and office.

【Ample Storage Space】There are 3 drawers and 3 cabinets with doors to ensure ample storage space for you. In addition, featuring 3 adjustable up-and-down 2.5-inch shelves, the kitchen storage cabinet is designed to provide you with plenty of private storage space for items of different sizes.

【Safe and Sturdy】For creating a safe environment for your family, this kitchen buffet cabinet is designed with an anti-tip device so you don't have to worry about your family's safety anymore. Additionally, made of high-quality metal hardware, which ensures the durability and solidity of the buffet sideboard.

【CARB Certification】CARB Phase 2 compliant: National standard in the U.S. instituted by the California Air Resources Board (CARB) to reduce formaldehyde emissions. Our panel of the kitchen buffet cabinet is certified by CARB with formaldehyde emission below 0.09 ppm. Therefore, this buffet sideboard is suitable for families with children and pets and has no negative effect on health.

【Easy Installation】According to the detailed instructions, this kitchen storage cabinet can be easily assembled. Our Cozy Castle is your 365-day good companion for any problem. Any question? Please do not hesitate to let us know and solve them. Over Dimension: 15.7"D x 47.2"W x 31.5"H

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 8, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Super cute, sturdy, and great customer service!
reviews.reviewText: Great purchase! My husband and I built this piece together in about an hour and a half and noticed the we received gold handles instead of the pictured black handles. I messaged the seller and they got back very quickly and sent an order of the black handles to our house free of charge and were very polite and apologetic about the mix up. The cabinet itself looks super cute just as pictured and seems to be sturdy with a lot of good storage room that we needed! Definitely would recommend this purchase.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 30, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Look at every piece before you put together!
reviews.reviewText: There was a lot of scratches and chips on this that I noticed, as I was putting it together. But overall it’s cute.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on June 28, 2023
reviews.reviewText: SUPER CUTE, perfect for a smaller kitchen and needing more storage space! It took a little while to build, but it was easy to follow along with the directions! Put on a movie or show and time flies easily!Note: the back board of the shelves are black and wood, you can decide which you want shown inside the drawers or on the backwall. i had to redo it because i placed it backwards the first time!soft closed cabinet doors are perfect, everything installed exactly like it was expected.would purchase again!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 18, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars a long time to put together
reviews.reviewText: directions were very confusing. took all day to put together and still had to just figure some things out because the directions were wrong. handles are also more of an orange color not gold. looks good though just changed out the handles

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 1, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Love the look of the product but the instructions and assembly were horrible. One cabinet door has already fallen off under a month of having the product. Looks great but be weary of assembly.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 4, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 1.0 out of 5 stars Don't buy, just don't buy this crappy cabinet
reviews.reviewText: I'm sure you will regret. Wrong installation instruction, wrong holes on the wrong side of panel, thin crappy materials, plastic door handles...etc.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 20, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Very shiny MDF wood and orange handles
reviews.reviewText: Was missing an entire box of necessary hardware and had to jump through hoops to get replacement parts. Finally received the missing parts but was disappointed in the wood finish. The material is a very shiny MDF wood and the handles are more of an orange gold. Will definitely have to switch out the handles. If you are looking for a more matte wood, this cabinet is definitely not it! Should’ve gone with something else!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 4, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 2.0 out of 5 stars Hardware Breaks Easily!
reviews.reviewText: It was a fairly good black friday deal however the hardware is absolute trash. The cam lock nuts break without even having to try. I would ask for a refund if it wouldn't be such a hassle but I went to home depot and bought better hardware to avoid having to return anything.
